<div class="rbp-service">
<section class="rbp-service-hero"><div class="rbp-service-c"><div class="rbp-service-hero-in"><div><div class="rbp-service-ey"><span class="rbp-service-dot"></span>{{ service_group }}</div><h1 class="rbp-service-h1">{{ page.title }}</h1><p class="rbp-service-p">{{ summary }}</p><div class="rbp-service-actions"><a class="rbp-service-btn rbp-service-btn-p" href="/pages/contact">Start an enquiry -&gt;</a><a class="rbp-service-btn rbp-service-btn-g" href="/pages/membership-options">View membership options</a></div><div class="rbp-service-proof"><span><span class="rbp-service-check">✓</span>{{ proof_1 }}</span><span><span class="rbp-service-check">✓</span>{{ proof_2 }}</span><span><span class="rbp-service-check">✓</span>{{ proof_3 }}</span></div></div><aside class="rbp-service-hero-card"><h3>{{ hero_card_title }}</h3><p>{{ hero_card_text }}</p></aside></div></div></section>
<section class="rbp-service-sec"><div class="rbp-service-c"><div class="rbp-service-grid rbp-service-g2"><div><div class="rbp-service-ey">Service overview</div><h2 class="rbp-service-h2">A practical service pathway for {{ page.title | downcase }}</h2><p class="rbp-service-p">{{ summary }}</p>{%- if page.content != blank -%}<div class="rbp-service-rich" style="margin-top:18px;">{{ page.content }}</div>{%- endif -%}</div><div class="rbp-service-card rbp-service-panel-blue"><h3 class="rbp-service-title">Best used when</h3><ul class="rbp-service-list"><li><span class="rbp-service-check">✓</span><span>{{ who_1 }}</span></li><li><span class="rbp-service-check">✓</span><span>{{ who_2 }}</span></li><li><span class="rbp-service-check">✓</span><span>{{ who_3 }}</span></li></ul></div></div></div></section>
<section class="rbp-service-sec rbp-service-muted"><div class="rbp-service-c"><div class="rbp-service-head"><div class="rbp-service-ey">Problems we solve</div><h2 class="rbp-service-h2">Built for real business friction</h2><p class="rbp-service-p">This service is designed to turn unclear requirements, stalled decisions and messy execution into a structured pathway.</p></div><div class="rbp-service-grid rbp-service-g3"><div class="rbp-service-card"><div class="rbp-service-icon">01</div><h3 class="rbp-service-title">{{ problem_1 }}</h3><p class="rbp-service-text">We help clarify the issue, define the decision point and identify what needs to happen next.</p></div><div class="rbp-service-card"><div class="rbp-service-icon">02</div><h3 class="rbp-service-title">{{ problem_2 }}</h3><p class="rbp-service-text">We provide practical structure, support and guidance so the work can move forward with less internal strain.</p></div><div class="rbp-service-card"><div class="rbp-service-icon">03</div><h3 class="rbp-service-title">{{ problem_3 }}</h3><p class="rbp-service-text">We focus on usable outputs, not decorative advice destined to rot in a folder.</p></div></div></div></section>
<section class="rbp-service-sec"><div class="rbp-service-c"><div class="rbp-service-head"><div class="rbp-service-ey">Outcomes</div><h2 class="rbp-service-h2">What you should walk away with</h2></div><div class="rbp-service-grid rbp-service-g3"><div class="rbp-service-card"><div class="rbp-service-icon">A</div><h3 class="rbp-service-title">{{ outcome_1 }}</h3><p class="rbp-service-text">A more structured understanding of the situation and the next decision to make.</p></div><div class="rbp-service-card"><div class="rbp-service-icon">B</div><h3 class="rbp-service-title">{{ outcome_2 }}</h3><p class="rbp-service-text">Practical guidance, outputs or recommendations that can be used inside the business.</p></div><div class="rbp-service-card"><div class="rbp-service-icon">C</div><h3 class="rbp-service-title">{{ outcome_3 }}</h3><p class="rbp-service-text">A clearer pathway for action, implementation or additional support.</p></div></div></div></section>
<section class="rbp-service-sec rbp-service-muted"><div class="rbp-service-c"><div class="rbp-service-grid rbp-service-g2"><div class="rbp-service-card"><div class="rbp-service-ey">Inclusions</div><h2 class="rbp-service-h2">What may be included</h2><ul class="rbp-service-list"><li><span class="rbp-service-check">✓</span><span>{{ inclusion_1 }}</span></li><li><span class="rbp-service-check">✓</span><span>{{ inclusion_2 }}</span></li><li><span class="rbp-service-check">✓</span><span>{{ inclusion_3 }}</span></li><li><span class="rbp-service-check">✓</span><span>{{ inclusion_4 }}</span></li></ul></div><div class="rbp-service-card"><div class="rbp-service-ey">Engagement process</div><h2 class="rbp-service-h2">How it works</h2><div class="rbp-service-step"><span class="rbp-service-step-num">01</span><h3>Submit your enquiry</h3><p>Share the service area, business context and outcome you need.</p></div><div class="rbp-service-step"><span class="rbp-service-step-num">02</span><h3>We review and scope</h3><p>The request is assessed so the right pathway, deliverables and next steps can be identified.</p></div><div class="rbp-service-step"><span class="rbp-service-step-num">03</span><h3>Service delivery begins</h3><p>We deliver the agreed support, documents, recommendations or implementation pathway.</p></div><div class="rbp-service-step"><span class="rbp-service-step-num">04</span><h3>Review and next steps</h3><p>You review the outcome and decide whether to proceed, refine or extend the engagement.</p></div></div></div></div></section>
