<section class="rbp-service-sec rbp-service-muted"><div class="rbp-service-c"><div class="rbp-service-grid rbp-service-g2"><div><div class="rbp-service-ey">FAQ</div><h2 class="rbp-service-h2">Common questions</h2><p class="rbp-service-p">The details depend on the service request, but these answers explain the usual engagement logic.</p></div><div class="rbp-service-faq"><details open><summary>How do I start?</summary><div>Use the enquiry form and include the service area, business context, urgency and desired outcome.</div></details><details><summary>Is this a fixed package or scoped service?</summary><div>Some services can be packaged, while others need scoping based on the business issue, complexity and deliverables required.</div></details><details><summary>Do I need to be a member?</summary><div>You can submit an enquiry without being a member. Membership may provide access to additional inclusions or support pathways.</div></details><details><summary>What happens after I submit an enquiry?</summary><div>Your request is reviewed, routed to the relevant pathway and responded to with next steps.</div></details></div></div></div></section>
